{
  "text": "Could you tell me how you are able to give us information like this with respect to the first distortion or Law of Confusion? I am Ra. Each of those is already aware of this information. Any other reader may extract the heart of meaning from this discussion without interest as to the examples' sources. If each was not fully aware of these answers we could not speak. It is interesting that in many of your queries you ask for confirmation rather than information. This is acceptable to us.",
